698
01:07:07,201 --> 01:07:09,572
Well, I expect he'll cope.

699
01:07:09,672 --> 01:07:13,875
And physics is back in business.

700
01:07:13,975 --> 01:07:15,307
Yes.

701
01:07:16,744 --> 01:07:19,324
Physics is back in business.

