I know you hate flying.

794
01:17:44,208 --> 01:17:46,377
I do hate to fly.

795
01:17:46,477 --> 01:17:49,046
Bring the car.

796
01:17:49,146 --> 01:17:52,985
Meet me in Bordeaux.

797
01:17:54,385 --> 01:17:58,059
Take the children camping.

798
