01:32:32,348 --> 01:32:34,036
Tea.

892
01:32:34,617 --> 01:32:36,155
You want a cup of tea.

893
01:32:39,455 --> 01:32:40,639
Okay.

894
01:32:44,594 --> 01:32:46,233
Any preference?

895
01:32:49,333 --> 01:32:52,338
You've memorized the board,
I know you have.

896
